name: Tezotubbie V1 Purple
description:
Tezotubbies are here! This is the 1st Version of the Green Tezotubbie born on Hic Et Nunc. Only 1/1 editions available for each. 

TezoTubbies is a creation of pixel art made with Tezos in mind and love at hand. The initial variation is 1/1. Hoping to grow and improve this project alongside our blockchain.
